ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>
[Low pathogenic avian influenza (LPAI) has periodically cropped up in
live bird markets in the northeastern US. Generally, it has been an
H7 variety. Based upon statements in the article, it is likely an
LPAI. - Mod.TG]
